{
  "stem": "2620.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, I see a bulletin-- 'Children under 18 should register.' And they'll take 'em to America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But belonging to a kibbutz and going to meetings, you become indoctrinated to go to Palestine, to build a homeland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when I saw the-- that bulletin, I didn't rush right away to register.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in fact, the thought occurred to me to tear that down, that other children my age and younger shouldn't see it-- shouldn't be tempted to go to America.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But instead, what I-- I didn't tear it down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That evening, when I went to sleep, I was doing some thinking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I says, who knows how much longer am I gonna have to be here before I can go?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I wanted to get out of Europe in the worst way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when I made up my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm gonna register.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But with this in mind, wherever is gonna come up first, that's where I will go, as long as I get out of here.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it came up for me to go to America first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is-- so I-- I-- I wind up over here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took me-- from the time we separated in Budapest, with my brother-- it took me five years to get in touch with him again.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I wind up-- I lived in Pittsburgh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day, I see-- I was reading a magazine-- the Jewish-- called the It's a Jewish magazine, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was an ad, children, I mean, people who are still looking for-- for a family should write to New York to this and this address.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wrote.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I gave all the information about my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at first, I used to get letters from people-- not my brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
